<p><a name="Other_awards" id="Other_awards"></a></p>
<h3><span class="editsection">[<a href="/w/index.php?title=2001:_A_Space_Odyssey_(film)&amp;action=edit&amp;section=17" title="Edit section: Other awards">edit</a>]</span> <span class="mw-headline">Other awards</span></h3>
<p><a name="Won" id="Won"></a></p>
